Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?Completar=20Armas=20(undo/redo+export),=20a?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=C3=B1adir=20m=C3=B3dulo=20Armaduras=20y=20migrar=20Objetos=20a?=
